SELECT workflow_uuid
        FROM "dbos".workflow_status
        WHERE status = $1
          AND queue_name = $2
          AND (application_version IS NULL OR application_version = $3)
          
        ORDER BY created_at ASC
        
        FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
